3DObstacleGame

To run:

make
./3DObstacle

This submission contains a fixed obstacle course with blocks moving up and down.
The character adjusts its position according to the height/depth of the block it is on.

The character is moved using the arrow keys and currently cannot move out of the play area.
Two camera views have been implemented.
Tower view which can be activated by pressing key S.
Top view which is the default view and can be activated by pressing key A.

The camera can be moved along the X, Y and Z axes.
To control movement along X axis use keys K and L.
To control movement along Y axis use keys R and T.
To control movement along Z axis use keys O and P. (This gives a zoom effect)

When appropriately used, one can rotate the camera using the above keys.
